This paper is about a new dataset for document-level relation extraction, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. The paper discusses the challenges of document-level RE and evaluates state-of-the-art methods on the dataset. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related topics. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these sub-categories also cover topics related to NLP and machine learning.
